# Kest CLI - Advanced Features Demo
# This file demonstrates all 4 new powerful features

## Feature 1: Duration Assertion (Performance Testing)
# Assert that API responds within 2 seconds
get https://httpbin.org/uuid --max-duration 2000

## Feature 2: Retry Mechanism (Reliability)
# Retry up to 3 times with 1-second intervals for flaky endpoints
post https://httpbin.org/post -d '{"demo": "retry"}' --retry 3 --retry-wait 1000

## Feature 3: More Tests for Parallel Demo
get https://httpbin.org/get
get https://httpbin.org/headers
get https://httpbin.org/user-agent
post https://httpbin.org/anything -d '{"test": "parallel"}'

## Feature 4: Test Summary (automatically shows at the end)
# Run with: kest run demo.kest
# Run with: kest run demo.kest --parallel --jobs 8 (FAST!)
